snippet.title: Vox Populi: Polska 2023 - Trailer
snippet.description:
Vox Populi: Polska 2023 available now on Steam!

Play as an existing or fully customisable political figure, and campaign for the Polish parliamentary election of 2023! In "Vox Populi: Poland 2023", you and the characters around you must promote your ideas and your popularity throughout the country to claim victory!
